nz.co.abrahams.asithappens
Class SNMPAccess

java.lang.Object
  nz.co.abrahams.asithappens.SNMPAccess

public class SNMPAccess
extends java.lang.Object

SNMP interface. This uses SNMP4J as the underlying SNMP access method, although this is hidden from calling clients.
